snippet.title: My Musical Romance: Episode 1
snippet.description:
A heart warming love story, full of drama!

You are going to revive the musical company that gave you the dreams of becoming an actress…but of course it’s not going to be easy!
Will you be able to unite the three cool actors together to overcome the difficulties awaiting ahead?
A heart warming love story, full of drama! 

■ Plot
When you are on the verge of giving up your dreams to become an actress, you happen to meet three handsome men.  
You decide to create a new musical company with them, in respect of a legendary company that for some reason disbanded.  
However, each man seems to have a problem of his own, and one trouble happens after another.  
Will you be able to make your dreams come true? Or was it an impossible challenge from the beginning?

APK link:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.genius.musical

By. Genius Inc.
